window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Mana is changing the world faster than people can adapt.</b><br> <br> It's happened before.<br> <br> Mutations are accelerating. The countdown to collapse won’t stop.<br> <br> This time, Len and Rick aren’t just surviving it—<b>they’re building something that can.</b><br> <br> But they can’t do it alone.<br> <br> From shattered coasts to rising strongholds, they’re hunting the people who mattered—the future legends, tacticians, and builders who once helped humanity endure.<br> <br> They remember who lived. They remember who died.<br> <br> And this time... they plan to save them before the end begins.</p> <p><b>You can’t stop the apocalypse alone. It's time for the Titans to rise once more.</b></p>"; 
